  m_text: 'Maid: States if a character is a ghost. Will always select subjects if
    lying, or ghosts if telling the truth


    Nun: States two potential subjects
    the ghost could be. One or both of the subjects could be ghosts. If lying, neither
    will be ghosts


    Jester: Either the Jester or another subject is the ghost.
    If the chosen subject isnt the ghost, then the Jester is lying


    Queen: States
    if they are next to at least one ghost. Could be one ghost and one subject, or
    two subjects'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
